message: I know this is pretty typical... But this is how we get the conversation started. What are your MUST READ webcomics?
every time they publish I read Dr. McNinja, Questionable Content, Achewood, Penny Arcade, and xkcd
If you like the writing in QC you should check out dieselsweeties.com
I used to be a regular Diesel Sweeties, scary go round, qwantz, something positive, and misfile reader, but too many plot lines to keep track of
@mwhooker yeah SGR got crazy to keep track of. loved the art... and the girls!

I love story comics, but between an an employer against personal Internet use and no memory to check on my iPhone I tend to just see xkcd, The Oatmeal and a couple randoms that don't mind me missing days/weeks.
